history.content:
(10/24 update)

Enrollment for CS C100 is working normally again. Students are able to both enroll and wait list.

--------

(original post) Many students have reported being unable to enroll or wait list into CS C100 today. I've tracked the problem to the 999 discussion section but am unable to resolve it myself so I've submitted a help desk ticket asking for help to fix this.

WE ARE AWARE OF THE PROBLEM.

As soon as I have any update, and/or the issue is resolved, I will post here to let you know it's okay to try enrolling again.
